data.Amber Index (AI): Amber Index (AI) reflects the price for 1kg of all listed amber goods based on the estimated market share of each type of amber. The Amber Index is calculated as:   (Baltic Index x Volume Mined + Ukranian Index x Volume Mined + Dominican Index x Volume Mined + Chiapas Index x Volume Mined + Sumatra Index x Volume Mined) / Total Volume Mined.
data.Baltic Index: Weighted index reflecting the price of 1kg of Baltic amber, calculated as 66.66% Baltic Rough Index (BR) and 33.33% Baltic Beads Index (BB).
data.Baltic Rough (BR): B -Baltic Amber; R - Rough: Weighted index reflecting the price of 1kg of Baltic amber rough, calculated as 10% Index for Baltic Rough Large Fractions Mex (BRLM) and 90% Index for Baltic Rough Medium Fractions Mix (BRMM).
data.BRLM: B -Baltic Amber; R - Rough ; L - Large Fractions (100 - 1000g); М - Mix : Weighted index reflecting the price of 1kg of Baltic amber rough of large fractions and mixed quality (33% AAA, 33% A, 33% B).
data.BRMM: B -Baltic Amber; R - Rough ; M - Medium Fractions (2-100g); М - Mix  : Weighted index reflecting the price of 1kg of Baltic amber rough of medium fractions and mixed quality (33% AAA, 33% A, 33% B).
data.BRMAAA: B -Baltic Amber; R - Rough ; M - Medium Fractions (2-100g); AAA - AAA Quality : Index reflects the price of 1kg of top quality (AAA) Baltic amber rough of medium fractions.
data.BRMA: B -Baltic Amber; R - Rough ; M - Medium Fractions (2-100g); A - A Quality : Index reflects the price of 1kg of medium quality (A) Baltic amber rough of medium fractions.
data.BRMB: B -Baltic Amber; R - Rough ; M - Medium Fractions (2-100g); B - B Quality : Index reflects the price of 1kg of low quality (B) Baltic amber rough of medium fractions.
data.BRMC: B -Baltic Amber; R - Rough ; M - Medium Fractions (2-100g); C - C Quality : Index reflects the price of 1kg of slag quality (C) Baltic amber rough of medium fractions.
data.BRMMBO: B -Baltic Amber; R - Rough ; M - Medium Fractions (2-100g) ; B - Beadable ; O - Opaque  : Index reflects the price of 1kg of Beadable and Opaque Baltic amber rough in medium fraction size.
data.BRMMBT: B -Baltic Amber; R - Rough ; M - Medium Fractions (2-100g) ; B - Beadable ; T- Transparent : Index reflects the price of 1kg of Beadable and Transparent Baltic amber rough in medium fraction size.
data.BRMMFO: B -Baltic Amber; R - Rough ; M - Medium Fractions (2-100g) ; F - Flat ; O - Opaque  : Index reflects the price of 1kg of Flat and Opaque Baltic amber rough in medium fraction size.
data.BRMMFT: B -Baltic Amber; R - Rough ; M - Medium Fractions (2-100g) ; F - Flat ; T- Transparent : Index reflects the price of 1kg of Flat and Transparent Baltic amber rough in medium fraction size.
data.Baltic Beads (BB): B -Baltic Amber; B - Beads : Weighted index reflects the price of 1kg of beads of Baltic amber, calculated as 10% top quality (5% BBAAAO and 5%BBAAAT) and 90% medium quality (45% BBAO and 45% BBAT).
data.BBAAAO: B -Baltic Amber; B - Beads; AAA - AAA Quality; O - Opaque : Index reflects the price of 1kg of top quality (AAA), opaque Baltic amber beads.
data.BBAAAT: B -Baltic Amber; B - Beads; AAA - AAA Quality; T - Transparent : Index reflects the price of 1kg of top quality (AAA), transparent Baltic amber beads.
data.BBAO: B -Baltic Amber; B - Beads; A - A Quality; O - Opaque : Index reflects the price of 1kg of medium quality (A), opaque Baltic amber beads.
data.BBAT: B -Baltic Amber; B - Beads; A - A Quality; T - Transparent : Index reflects the price of 1kg of medium quality (A), transparent Baltic amber beads.
data.Ukranian Index: Weighted index reflecting the price of 1kg of Ukranian amber, calculated as 66.66% Ukranian Rough Index (BR) and 33.33% Ukranian Beads Index (BB).
data.Ukranian Rough (UR): U -Ukranian Amber; R - Rough: Weighted index reflecting the price of 1kg of Ukranian amber rough, calculated as 10% Index for Ukranian Rough Large Fractions Mex (URLM) and 90% Index for Ukranian Rough Medium Fractions Mix (URMM).
data.URLM: U -Ukranian Amber; R - Rough ; L - Large Fractions (100 - 1000g); М - Mix : Weighted index reflecting the price of 1kg of Ukranian amber rough of large fractions and mixed quality (33% AAA, 33% A, 33% B).
data.URMM: U -Ukranian Amber; R - Rough ; M - Medium Fractions (2-100g); М - Mix  : Weighted index reflecting the price of 1kg of Ukranian amber rough of medium fractions and mixed quality (33% AAA, 33% A, 33% B).
data.URMAAA: U -Ukranian Amber; R - Rough ; M - Medium Fractions (2-100g); AAA - AAA Quality : Index reflects the price of 1kg of top quality (AAA) Ukranian amber rough of medium fractions.
data.URMA: U -Ukranian Amber; R - Rough ; M - Medium Fractions (2-100g); A - A Quality : Index reflects the price of 1kg of medium quality (A) Ukranian amber rough of medium fractions.
data.URMB: U -Ukranian Amber; R - Rough ; M - Medium Fractions (2-100g); B - B Quality : Index reflects the price of 1kg of low quality (B) Ukranian amber rough of medium fractions.
data.URMC: B -Ukranian Amber; R - Rough ; M - Medium Fractions (2-100g); C - C Quality : Index reflects the price of 1kg of slag quality (C) Ukranian amber rough of medium fractions.
data.URMMBO: U -Ukranian Amber; R - Rough ; M - Medium Fractions (2-100g) ; B - Beadable ; O - Opaque  : Index reflects the price of 1kg of Beadable and Opaque Ukranian amber rough in medium fraction size.
data.URMMBT: U -Ukranian Amber; R - Rough ; M - Medium Fractions (2-100g) ; B - Beadable ; T- Transparent : Index reflects the price of 1kg of Beadable and Transparent Ukranian amber rough in medium fraction size.
data.URMMFO: U -Ukranian Amber; R - Rough ; M - Medium Fractions (2-100g) ; F - Flat ; O - Opaque  : Index reflects the price of 1kg of Flat and Opaque Ukranian amber rough in medium fraction size.
data.URMMFT: U -Ukranian Amber; R - Rough ; M - Medium Fractions (2-100g) ; F - Flat ; T- Transparent : Index reflects the price of 1kg of Flat and Transparent Ukranian amber rough in medium fraction size.
data.Ukranian Beads (UB): U -Ukranian Amber; B - Beads : Weighted index reflects the price of 1kg of beads of Ukranian amber, calculated as 10% top quality (5% UBAAAO and 5%UBAAAT) and 90% medium quality (45% UBAO and 45% UBAT).
data.UBAAAO: U -Ukranian Amber; B - Beads; AAA - AAA Quality; O - Opaque : Index reflects the price of 1kg of top quality (AAA), opaque Ukranian amber beads.
data.UBAAAT: U -Ukranian Amber; B - Beads; AAA - AAA Quality; T - Transparent : Index reflects the price of 1kg of top quality (AAA), transparent Ukranian amber beads.
data.UBAO: U -Ukranian Amber; B - Beads; A - A Quality; O - Opaque : Index reflects the price of 1kg of medium quality (A), opaque Ukranian amber beads.
data.UBAT: U -Ukranian Amber; B - Beads; A - A Quality; T - Transparent : Index reflects the price of 1kg of medium quality (A), transparent Ukranian amber beads.
data.Chiapas Index: Weighted index reflecting the price of 1kg of Chiapas amber. Due to a lack of prices on Chiapas rough, the index is estimated as 50% of Chiapas Beads index.
data.Chiapas Beads (CB): C - Chiapas; B - Beads : Weighted index reflecting the price of 1kg of Chiapas amber beads, based on 33% CBAAA, 33% CBAA, and 33% CBA.
data.CBAAA: C - Chiapas; B - Beads; AAA - AAA Quality : Index reflects the price of 1kg of top quality (AAA) beads of Chiapas amber.
data.CBAA: C - Chiapas; B - Beads; AA - AA Quality : Index reflects the price of 1kg of better quality (AA) beads of Chiapas amber.
data.CBA: C - Chiapas; B - Beads; A - A Quality : Index reflects the price of 1kg of medium quality (A) beads of Chiapas amber.
data.Sumatra Index: Weighted index reflecting the price of 1kg of Sumatra amber, calculated as 66.66% Sumatra Rough Index (SR) and 33.33% Sumatra Beads Index (SB).
data.Sumatra Rough (SR): S - Sumatra; R - Rough : Weighted index reflecting the price of 1kg of Sumatra amber rough, calculated as 1% SRAAA, 10% SRAA and 89% SRA.
data.SRAAA: S - Sumatra; R - Rough; AAA - AAA Quality : Index reflects the price of 1kg of Sumatra amber of top quality (AAA).
data.SRAA: S - Sumatra; R - Rough; AA - AA Quality : Index reflects the price of 1kg of Sumatra amber of better quality (AA).
data.SRA: S - Sumatra; R - Rough; A - A Quality : Index reflects the price of 1kg of Sumatra amber of medium quality (A).
data.Sumatra Beads (SB): S - Sumatra; B - Beads : Weighted index reflecting the price of 1kg of Sumatra amber beads, calculated as 1% top quality (AAA), 10% better quality (AA) and 89% medium quality (A).
data.SBAAA: S - Sumatra; B - Beads; AAA - AAA Quality : Index reflects the price of 1kg of top quality (AAA) beads of Sumatra amber.
data.SBAA: S - Sumatra; B - Beads; AA - AA Quality : Index reflects the price of 1kg of better quality (AA) beads of Sumatra amber.
data.SBA: S - Sumatra; B - Beads; A - A Quality : Index reflects the price of 1kg of medium quality (A) beads of Sumatra amber.
data.Dominican Index: Weighted index reflecting the price of Dominican amber, calculated as 66.6% Dominican Rough Index (DR) and 33.3% Dominican Beads Index (DB).
data.Dominican Rough (DR): D -Dominican Amber ; R - Rough : Index reflect the price of 1kg of Dominican amber rough based on 33.3% DRBlue, 33.3% DRGreen, and 33.3% DRYellow.
data.DRBlue: D -Dominican Amber; R - Rough; B - Blue : Index reflecting the price of 1kg of blue Dominican amber rough.
data.DRGreen: D -Dominican Amber; R - Rough; G - Green : Index reflecting the price of 1kg of green Dominican amber rough.
data.DRYellow: D -Dominican Amber; R - Rough; Y - Yellow : Index reflecting the price of 1kg of yellow Dominican amber rough.
data.Dominican Beads (DB): D -Dominican Amber; B - Beads : Weighted index reflecting the price of 1kg of Dominican amber beads, calculated as 33.3% DBB, 33.3% DBG and 33.3% DBY.
data.DBB: D -Dominican Amber; B - Beads; B - Blue : Weighted index reflecting the price of 1kg of blue beads of Dominican amber, calculated as 20% AAA quality and 80% A quality.
data.DBG: D -Dominican Amber; B - Beads; G - Green : Weighted index reflecting the price of 1kg of green beads of Dominican amber, calculated as 20% AAA quality and 80% A quality.
data.DBY: D -Dominican Amber; B - Beads; Y - Yellow : Weighted index reflecting the price of 1kg of yellow beads of Dominican amber, calculated as 20% AAA quality and 80% A quality.
data.DBAAAB: D -Dominican Amber; B - Beads; AАА - AАА Quality; B - Blue : Index reflects the price of 1kg of blue color, AAA quality Dominican amber beads.
data.DBAAAG: D -Dominican Amber; B - Beads; ААA - ААA Quality; G - Green : Index reflects the price of 1kg of green color, AAA quality Dominican amber beads.
data.DBAAAY: D -Dominican Amber; B - Beads; AАА - ААA Quality; Y - Yellow : Index reflects the price of 1kg of yellow color, AAA quality Dominican amber beads.
data.DBAB: D -Dominican Amber; B - Beads; A - A Quality; B - Blue : Index reflects the price of 1kg of blue color, A quality Dominican amber beads.
data.DBAG: D -Dominican Amber; B - Beads; A - A Quality; G - Green : Index reflects the price of 1kg of green color, A quality Dominican amber beads.
data.DBAY: D -Dominican Amber; B - Beads; A - A Quality; Y - Yellow : Index reflects the price of 1kg of yellow color, A quality Dominican amber beads.
